[In the 24 hours from 11 to 12 Mar 2020, the number of cases of COVID-19 confirmed in Iran grew from 9000 to 10 075 an increase of 1075 newly confirmed cases. The number of deaths has also increased from 354 to 429, an increase of 75 deaths in the 24 hour period. It was very difficult to find a good report with the case counts today (12 Mar 2020).

