ProMED-mail
<promed@promedmail.org>

[Much of this is a repeat of the Director General's 11 Mar 2020 speech but definitely worth repeating. Every day when I am reformatting the tables for our post, I am struck by the number of countries that are most probably not "seeking" (remember my favorite adage "seek and ye shall find") one way or another, either only testing foreign nationals so all cases are imported cases, or are not checking for community spread when there is already identified local transmission. The key is to increase vigilance early on to interrupt transmission. - Mod.MPP]

