[Religious gatherings of multiple faiths and sects within the faiths have been foci of spread of the coronavirus. Examples include the major outbreak in South Korea related to a religious group that had recently built a church in Wuhan China; the 2 church associated clusters in Singapore; Qom, Iran a site of Shi'ite Muslim pilgrimage where the ongoing epidemic seemed to have started in Iran; and New York, New York, the index case for a growing cluster in Westchester county and New York City spread among synagogue attendees. We forget that these houses of worship are sites for mass gatherings. A challenge in this growing pandemic. - Mod.MPP

